 * Puerto fijo: 3000
 */

### Obtener todas las cookies
GET {{baseUrl}}/cookies
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Obtener cookies por tipo (siendo types un array, tu backend decidir치 si busca coincidencia)
GET {{baseUrl}}/cookies/type/vegana
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Obtener cookies por visibilidad (true/false)
GET {{baseUrl}}/cookies/visible/true
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### Crear una cookie nueva (campos reales del documento)
POST {{baseUrl}}/cookies
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cookie_name": "Red Velvet Cookie",
  "description": "Esta cookie es el sue침o de cualquier Red Velvet lover.",
  "types": [],
  "image_png": "red-velvet.png",
  "image_webp": "red-velvet.webp",
  "visible": true
}

###

### Actualizar una cookie por _id (PUT)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/cookies/{{cookieId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cookie_name": "Red Velvet Cookie (Updated)",
  "description": "Descripci칩n actualizada.",
  "types": ["red-velvet", "premium"],
  "image_png": "red-velvet.png",
  "image_webp": "red-velvet.webp",
  "visible": true
}

###

### Ocultar una cookie (si tu PUT permite actualizar parcial, esto funcionar치; si no, usa el body completo de arriba)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/cookies/{{cookieId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "visible": false
}

###

### Eliminar una cookie por _id
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/cookies/{{cookieId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}